<section id="readingText">
  <p align="left">Dear Sir/Madam,</p>
  <p align="left">I am writing to apologise for missing my 3 p.m. appointment with you on Thursday, 12th November.</p>
  <p align="left">I am terribly sorry but on my way to your office the taxi I <font color="#0000ff">[16] in <font color="#0000ff">[17]</font> with a bus. Although I only <font color="#0000ff">[18]</font> minor bruising, the taxi driver <font color="#0000ff">[19]</font> his head against the windscreen, <font color="#0000ff">[20]</font> it very badly and <font color="#0000ff">[21]</font> unconscious. Also, several of the passengers on the bus <font color="#0000ff">[22]</font> and <font color="#0000ff">[23]</font> to be taken to hospital. Although I <font color="#0000ff">[24]</font> myself, I <font color="#0000ff">[25]</font> to hospital. I <font color="#0000ff">[26]</font> any treatment but I was in a state of shock for a number of hours afterwards. I <font color="#0000ff">[28]</font> repeated attempts to contact your office but every time I <font color="#0000ff">[29]</font>, the line was engaged.</font></p>
  <p align="left">I would like to know if it would be possible to rearrange the appointment. I am free on Tuesday and Thursday afternoons, however, if I have enough notice, it would also be possible for me to rearrange my work schedule and meet at your convenience.</p>
  <p align="left">Thank you for your kind attention.</p>
