  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">When we recount something that happened in the past, we mainly use the past simple, and we often need to use passive as well as active voice. The past simple form (for active voice) and the past participle form (for passive voice) of many common verbs are irregular so make sure you know them!</font>
